					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Consignment Fundraising Live Auction Benefits for Galas]]></title>
		<link>https://impactauctions.org/2025/02/12/consignment-fundraising-live-auction-benefits-for-galas/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 15:39:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[liveimpactauctions]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://impactauctions.org/?p=5487</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Consignment trips are useful in fundraising galas because they offer <strong>high-value</strong> auction items with minimal financial risk to the organization. </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Here’s why they are effective:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>No Upfront Cost</strong> – The nonprofit only pays for the trip if it sells at auction, ensuring they don’t lose money on unsold items.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>High Appeal</strong> – Luxury vacations and unique travel experiences attract high bids, driving up revenue.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Exclusive Experiences</strong> – Many consignment companies offer trips that are hard to find elsewhere, making them desirable to bidders.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Increased Bidding Competition</strong> – Because the nonprofit can sell multiple packages, more than one bidder can win, maximizing fundraising potential.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Minimal Effort</strong> – The consignment company handles trip logistics, reducing the burden on the nonprofit’s team.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>By offering aspirational travel experiences without financial risk, consignment trips help fundraising galas raise more money while keeping expenses low.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Contact <a href="https://www.impactauctions.info/consignment-experiences/">IMPACT AUCTIONS </a>for your consignment needs.  </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:jetpack/slideshow {"ids":[5492,5495,5497],"sizeSlug":"full"} -->
<div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow aligncenter" data-effect="slide"><div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_container swiper-container"><ul class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_swiper-wrapper swiper-wrapper"><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-5492" data-id="5492" src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1787.jpeg" /><figcaption class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption">Screenshot</figcaption></figure></li><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-5495" data-id="5495" src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1794.jpeg" /><figcaption class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_caption gallery-caption">Screenshot</figcaption></figure></li><li class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_slide swiper-slide"><figure><img alt="" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_image wp-image-5497" data-id="5497" src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/galord-retreat.jpeg" /></figure></li></ul><a class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-prev swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white" role="button"></a><a class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-next swiper-button-next swiper-button-white" role="button"></a><a aria-label="Pause Slideshow" class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_button-pause" role="button"></a><div class="wp-block-jetpack-slideshow_pagination swiper-pagination swiper-pagination-white"></div></div></div>
<!-- /wp:jetpack/slideshow -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5499,"width":"179px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1993.jpeg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1993.jpeg?w=764" alt="" class="wp-image-5499" style="width:179px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"><a href="https://www.impactauctions.info">Impact Auctions</a> is here to help you today.  <sup data-fn="7d8a4312-9e51-4196-a08b-6492d3a440ae" class="fn"><a href="#7d8a4312-9e51-4196-a08b-6492d3a440ae" id="7d8a4312-9e51-4196-a08b-6492d3a440ae-link">1</a></sup><br><br>Take your FUNDRAISING EVENT to the Next Level<br>Ron and Debbie Hitzel, Founders of Impact Auctions, enjoy helping Non-Profit Organizations all over the United States reach their goals in Live &amp; Silent Auctions which includes Virtual Events, Fund Appeals, Consignment Trips, Event Planning, and Emcee.  Live Auctions for fundraising non-profit organizations are very popular because of the funds they raise in a short amount of time.  Impact Auctions is offering a Free Consultation for your next charity fundraising event that will guarantee your organization to reach your goal and exceed it.   Be ready to take your event to the next level with this talented team.  </figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:footnotes /-->]]></content:encoded>
