					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Impact Auctions Fundraising Auctioneer]]></title>
		<link>https://impactauctions.org/2025/04/07/impact-auctions-fundraising-auctioneer/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 17:19:40 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[liveimpactauctions]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://impactauctions.org/?p=5529</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:video {"guid":"77Rhiqty","id":5537,"poster":"https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_2917.jpg","videoPressClassNames":"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-videopress"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-video wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-videopress"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
https://videopress.com/v/77Rhiqty?resizeToParent=true&amp;cover=true&amp;posterUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fliveimpactauctions.wordpress.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fimg_2917.jpg&amp;preloadContent=metadata&amp;useAverageColor=true
</div><figcaption>Live Fundraising Auction </figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:video -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Impact Auctions is an upbeat Fundraising team for your next Fundraising gala.  </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Experience! Reliability! Expert!</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Debbie and Ron Hitzel, Impact Auctions, are a husband and wife team that have been in the fundraising business for over 20 years raising money for charitable causes close to their hearts. Our Auctioneer is a former US Navy Nuclear Submariner and has upgraded electrical power plants around the world and has his masters degree in business management. Ron speaks several languages after working in over 56 countries and thus brings his world travels to the stage! Debbie is a former teacher of almost 30 years and now enjoys helping all fundraising events. We look forward in helping your Next Non Profit Fundraising event.&nbsp;</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Impact Auctions has three Licensed Charity Auctioneers that have helped  thousands of organizations set&nbsp;record-breaking profits&nbsp;in one night with less work for the volunteers and committee members. &nbsp; </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5534,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_9640.jpeg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/img_9640.jpeg?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-5534" /></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Contact<a href="https://www.impactauctions.info"> Impact Auctions</a> today.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[]]></excerpt:encoded>
