					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Fundraising Gala 'WRAP UP" for the Year]]></title>
		<link>https://impactauctions.org/2025/10/28/fundraising-gala-wrap-up-for-the-year/</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Oct 2025 15:26:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[liveimpactauctions]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://impactauctions.org/?p=5581</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:image {"id":140,"width":"114px","height":"auto","sizeSlug":"full","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/unknown.jpeg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/unknown.jpeg" alt="" class="wp-image-140" style="width:114px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Fundraising Tips to ensure your next years gala's success.  </figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:group {"layout":{"type":"flex","flexWrap":"nowrap"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-group"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Can you believe we are coming to the end of the 2025 year already?  Next year's fundraising STARTS NOW.  What can we do to prepare for 2026.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Send a Year-End Impact Message</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Goal: Thank, celebrate, and remind donors of their impact.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Share a heartfelt letter or video from your founder or beneficiaries.<br>Include before-and-after stories or highlight a success that their donations made possible. Use warm, emotional language — “Because of you, we…”</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>🪩 Pro tip: Add a visual recap — a short slideshow or “year in review” reel — for use at galas, social media, and email.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>💌</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":2} -->
<ol start="2" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Launch a “Finish Strong” Giving Campaign</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Goal: Inspire one last wave of giving before December 31.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Tie the theme to your mission (e.g., “Light Up a Life Before the New Year”).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><br>Offer donation matches or “sponsor a table” gift challenges.<br>Use countdown-style emails (“3 Days Left to Make Your Impact”).</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>🪙 Pro tip: Include QR codes at your gala and on social media that lead directly to your donation form.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>🥂</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":3} -->
<ol start="3" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Celebrate with a Year-End Gala or Appreciation Event</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Goal: Thank supporters and keep energy high for next year.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Recognize top donors, volunteers, or partners with awards.<br>Feature a short video recap of your nonprofit’s 2025 wins.<br>Have a “Fund the Future” live auction or paddle raise focused on 2026 goals.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>🕊️ Pro tip: Make the event fun and emotional — people give more when they feel connected to a story.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>📣</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":4} -->
<ol start="4" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Engage Your Donors Digitally</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Goal: Stay visible through the holidays.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Post “12 Days of Impact” or “Countdown to Kindness” stories on social media.<br>Share donor spotlights or testimonials.<br>Update your website with your “Year in Review” and “2026 Vision.”</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>📱 Pro tip: Always include donation links and event sign-up buttons.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>✨</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true,"start":5} -->
<ol start="5" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li><strong>Thank Generously &amp; Preview Next Year</strong></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Goal: End with gratitude and anticipation.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Send personal thank-yous to major donors before New Year’s Eve.<br>Announce next year’s gala theme, date, or campaign focus.<br>Create a short video invitation or “save the date” teaser.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Example:  As we look ahead to 2026, we invite you to celebrate with us at our Gala and help us reach even greater heights.  Please Save the date __________</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The year may be coming to a close, but Fundraising never ends!!!!!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5441,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_7781-1.jpg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_7781-1.jpg?w=720" alt="" class="wp-image-5441" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Giving continues throughout the year. <br><br>Contact Debbie with Impact Auctions today by using this link: <a href="https://www.impactauctions.info/contact-us/"> https://www.impactauctions.info/contact-us/</a></figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5585,"width":"248px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"1.0084216245585438","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_0754.jpeg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/img_0754.jpeg?w=720" alt="" class="wp-image-5585" style="aspect-ratio:1.0084216245585438;width:248px;height:auto" /></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
