					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[VIP Fundraising:  Gala Tips]]></title>
		<link>https://impactauctions.org/2026/02/06/add-a-vip-hour-at-the-fundraising-gala/</link>
		<pubDate>Fri, 06 Feb 2026 15:52:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[liveimpactauctions]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://impactauctions.org/?p=5613</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Why a VIP Hour Before a Fundraising Gala Matters</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><em>“VIP Hour turns donors into partners, sets the emotional tone, builds early momentum, and creates a calm, elevated experience that drives giving before the gala even begins.”</em> <em>Impact Auctions</em></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5620,"width":"304px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7484566559429615","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/img_4462.jpeg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/img_4462.jpeg?w=699" alt="" class="wp-image-5620" style="aspect-ratio:0.7484566559429615;width:304px;height:auto" /></a><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Screenshot</figcaption></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Let's dig a little deeper why it can set your event apart from others.  </p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>1️⃣ It Deepens Donor Relationships</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>VIP Hour creates space for meaningful connection before the room gets loud and busy.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Major donors feel seen and valued.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Board members can actually talk to guests.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Sponsors get personal access to leadership.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>It shifts donors from “attendees” to “partners.”</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>People don’t give to events — they give to relationships.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>2️⃣ It Increases Giving Before the Auction Starts</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>A relaxed environment opens wallets.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Guests preview auction items calmly.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Staff can point out high-value packages.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>You can quietly plant bidding interest early.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Donors begin emotionally committing before the program starts.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>By the time the ballroom fills, VIP guests are already invested.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>3️⃣ It Builds Exclusivity and Prestige</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>VIP Hour makes people feel special — and people pay for that.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Creates a sense of “inner circle.”</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Encourages higher ticket tiers.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Sponsors see more value in upgrades.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Donors want to return next year at the same or higher level.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>It turns a gala into an experience, not just a dinner.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>4️⃣ It Reduces Stress During the Main Event</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Instead of chaos later:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Check-in is smoother.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Items are already understood.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Guests know the mission story before the lights go down.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Big bidders are already warmed up.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Your main program runs cleaner and faster.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>5️⃣ It Sets the Emotional Tone</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>VIP Hour isn’t about hype — it’s about heart.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Guests connect to the mission early.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>They hear stories, not just announcements.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>They walk into the ballroom already aligned with purpose.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>When emotion is set early, fundraising feels natural later.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🥂 What a VIP Hour Should Look Like</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Think: elegant, intimate, intentional.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>⏰ Timing</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>45–60 minutes before general doors open.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Quiet, unrushed, no blasting music yet.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🍸 Atmosphere</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Passed champagne, wine, signature cocktail.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Soft live music or instrumental playlist.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Comfortable seating clusters.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Good lighting (warm, not stage bright).</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🖼 Auction Preview</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>High-value items displayed with staff nearby.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Impact Auctions team quietly guiding interest:<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>“This one usually closes high.”</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>“We already have two donors excited about this.”</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Tablets ready for early favorites, not heavy bidding yet.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🤝 Intentional Networking</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Not random mingling — curated moments.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Board members assigned to hosts.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Sponsors introduced to leadership.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Top donors introduced to beneficiaries (if appropriate).</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Short personal conversations, not speeches.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Photo opportunity with Special Guests</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🎤 Micro-Moments (Optional but powerful)</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Instead of a full program:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A 3-minute welcome from CEO or Chair.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>One emotional mission story.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A simple thank-you to VIP guests for believing in the cause.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Keep it short and heartfelt.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>🎁 VIP Touches</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Small things go far:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Name badges with ribbon.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>A printed “VIP Preview Guide.”</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Early access to special items.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Reserved seating revealed later.</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>VIP Hour should feel calm, classy, and personal.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>💰 How VIP Hour Helps Impact Auctions Specifically</strong></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>In many galas, 30–40% of revenue comes from people in that VIP room.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Want more creative ideas? Contact Debbie.   <a href="https://www.impactauctions.info">https://www.impactauctions.info</a></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:image {"id":5610,"width":"294px","height":"auto","aspectRatio":"0.7507904319574366","sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"media"} -->
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><a href="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/img_1509.jpg"><img src="https://liveimpactauctions.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/img_1509.jpg?w=720" alt="" class="wp-image-5610" style="aspect-ratio:0.7507904319574366;width:294px;height:auto" /></a></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p></p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
